\subsubsection{The Adventurer's Guild will bank money and/or valuables
at a fee of 2 Silver Pennies per 500 ounces per month.}

If money and/or valuables deposited with the Guild has a weight not
divisible by 500, round up to the nearest five-hundred weight.  A
guildmember pays one-half the price to bank with the guild.

The Guild will place money and/or valuables in safekeeping until the
depositor redeems their property, or until the value of the deposit
covers the banking fee.  The Guild does not extend credit when it
comes to banking fees.

